                        <interp inst="t18380101-name-827" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN ROBERTS</persName>
                  </hi>. I deal-with Mr. Jenkins—I know the prisoner by being his servant—on Saturday afternoon, between four and five o'clock, I paid him 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. which I owed him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
