                        <interp inst="t18380101-name-829" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WILLIAMSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I reside next door to the prosecutor—the pri<lb></lb>soner has been in the habit of bringing beer to me—he came in and in<lb></lb>quired for my young man, and said he owed him for a pint of beer—I said he was not at home, but he would not be long—he said he intended to leave his master and take what money he could get with him—I went and told Mr. Jenkins of it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> You told me he had left the place and ran away. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> No, I did not—I said he would be in shortly.</p>
